\id DAN Kyaka Enga Shorter Bible, SF codes August 20, 93
\h DANIELE
\toc1 DANIELE
\toc2 Daniele
\toc3 Dan
\mt1 DANIELE
\ip Buku dake Juu wambu dupwa kiŋi wakale Anatu suu pyaa nange mendeme randa maiyuo pyao puu maiyuo kareyaminyipa lekeleke rao kareyaminyi yuu gii mendepa piya. Pii repa repape sinju piipi dupwame wambu dupwa mona porainyi pyambuo kiŋi wakale doko Anatumi isa nembaramopa nakama range wambunya mende iso karara lao lamaiya.
\ip Pii lama ingyuo liti pyuo palamo.
\io1 \bk 1. Rombo 1-7 \bk*Juu akali yuu wakalena karapusi kareyami dokona mende Daniele lenge dokope banya puu minyingi dupwa pipya Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao baa leyamuli pyuo piyaminyi dokome nakamana yanda pimwai wambu dupwa nyuo anamasi minyiyami. Arome pii dasipa yuu Bapilone wambu dupwame iso karo dee yuu Pesa wambu dupwame iso karo piyaminyi yuu gii dokopa pyao reteyami.
\io1 \bk 2. Rombo 8-12 \bk*Daniele baame kongwalu pii kisima pii repa repa pyuo kandeya. Doko wambu rara wakale wakale dupwame porayapala yango duwpa nyuo isa palyuo kareyaminyi dupwa Bapilone kanda seramopa isa pyakara pyakara pirami renge doko lasaka piyami. Kongwalu pii dasipana dopa pyuo wambu doo Anatunya wambu randa maingi dupwa isa pyakaraminyipa Anatunya wambu dupwa keta ingyuo kararami dokona nolakao lao buku dakena lao pyasi palamo.
\ip Daniele baa ateŋa lenge akali ingyuo karo Anatu keta renge renge soo kareya.
\c 1
\s1 Isaraele Wane Parange Dusipa Kiŋi Nepukatenesana Anda Dokona Kareyami
\p 
\v 1 Ee kana repo dokona akali Jiyoakwimi doko Juta wambunya kiŋi ingyuo kareyamo dokopa yuu Bapilone dokona kiŋi Nepukatenesame yuu Jerusaleme pyao nyuo kako piya.
\v 2 Kamongo dokome kiŋi Nepukatenesame kiŋi Jiyoakwimipa tembole anda bange keyange singi dupwana lapope nyinya leya. Baame wambu lapo karapusi ingyuo nyuo minyuo mee bange anatuŋu lao lakandenge dupwana tembole anda yuu Bapilone dokona lanyuo peya. Dee bange keyange nyiyamo dupwa tembole anda dokona bange retenge panda dokona reteya.
\p 
\v 3 Dokopa kiŋi dokome akali Asepenase banya isingi akali mupwa doko lamaiyuo, Isaraele akali karapusi palaminyi dokona kiŋinya ree palu dupwanape wambu mupwa ingyuo karenge dupwanape wane parange lapo rombo palyuo nyepe, leya.
\v 4 Nakama wane au pingipi dee nakamana yanenge dokona koo mende pali nao suu pingi keyange palyuo sukuli andake mana nyisipi dee wane waiya lao soo nyingipi dupwa kapa ingyuo kiŋinya anda dokona yulu pyuo kararami lao rombo palyuo nyepe, leya. Akali Asepenase dokome nakama yuu Bapilone rangena pii yaka laowape pepa pyaowape kararami lao mana lamaira ingiya.
\v 5 Dokopa wambu kiŋi dokona anda palyuo nengepe ipwa waenepe neyaminyi doko suu pyao yuu peparae nenge mendare dopako pyuo wane dusipa nena lao lamaiya. Dokopa sukuli mana nyuo karo ee kana rema epo paparamopa nakama kiŋinya lenge kambu sera dokona kandena lao epo kararami, leya.
\v 6 Wane angi rombo palyiyamo dupwana wane mende kingi Daniele lenge mende Ananaya lenge dee mende Misaele lenge dee mende Asaraya lenge. Nakama peparae Jutana rara dokona ingyuo kareyami.
\v 7 Dokopa akali isingi mupwa dokome wane dusipa kingi wakale enenge leya. Wane mende kingi Beletesasa mende Satarake mende Mesake dee mende Apeneko leya.
\p 
\v 8 Dokopa kiŋinya anda nenge neyaminyi dokome Daniele banya yongo doko kokwa sasaroŋo naa naro lao suu pyaro kareya. Dopa pipala akali isingi mupwa Asepenase dokome baa nyisinya lao piso siya.
\v 9 Dokopa akali Asepenase doko Anatumi nyisiyamosa baame Daniele kando sakame kumuo nyisalana suu piya.
\v 10 Suu pyapala Asepenaseme kiŋi dokona lao pakapala Daniele lamaiyuo, Kiŋi dokome nakama nenge ipwape naramiŋi lapyamo doko lao oto lapyasa pipya. Dee wane yango menge dupwa nenge ipwape kapa napala kararaminyipa nakama lopo lenge kambu nyero kararaminyisa kandapala namba pyao kumakasara, leya.
\p 
\v 11 Dopa leyamo dokopa Asepenaseme isingi akali mendeme wane rema dusipape dee Danielepe iso karena lao rombo palyiyamo doko kareyamo dokona Daniele peya.
\v 12 Papala baame lao, Namwa ipwa nenge awape iki yuu gii akalisa nalapa lao joo embame makande pyuo kandape, leya.
\v 13 Dokopa wane parange kiŋinya anda nenge angi nao karaminyi dupwa pipya namwa pyasapala api kapa au pyuo karamipi lao kandapala embame langiri, leya.
\p 
\v 14 Dopa leyamopa akali nakamana isingi dokome yuu gii akalisa iki makande pyuo nenge awa ipwape iki nena leya.
\v 15 Yuu gii akalisa dusipa epo papeyamo dokopa wane dolosipame wane menge kiŋinya nenge porai neyami dupwa isa palyuo yongo keyange karo porai ingyuo kareyami.
\v 16 Dokona lao isingi akali dokome kiŋinya nenge porai maiya nao ipwa nenge awape dupwa iki maiya.
\p 
\v 17 Dokopa Anatumi akali parange kisima dusipa soo nyinginya renge maiyuo buku yaka lenge dupwana mora piso elyape inginyi pyambuo dee renge wakale wakale angi dupwana soo gisinya lao maiyuo piya. Dopa pipala baame Daniele pii repa repa pingipi dee kombeya pingipi dupwana renge angi polo lara lao suu pingi keyange maiya.
\p 
\v 18 Ee kana rema dusipa epo papeyamo dokopa kiŋinya lao reteyamo dokona palyuo isingi akali Asepenaseme wane parange dupwa peparae lanyuo Nepukatenesa peteyamo dokona peya.
\v 19 Peyamo dokopa kiŋi dokome peparae pii lamaiyuo karo kandeyamo dokopa wane menge dupwa nyuo isa palyuo wane Danielemoo Ananayamoo Misaelemoo Asarayamoo dusipa kamame ulipili mupwa ingiyamo kando nyiya. Nyepala dokona lao nakama kiŋinya anda dokona ree palu ingyuo kareyami.
\v 20 Dokopa kiŋi dokome piso singi pii mendepe dee randa mendepe sipureyamopa mali mali sakangepe nemonga lenge dupwape nyuo isa palyuo wane parange dusipame kamame ulipili ingyuo renge dupwana konda pyuo soo nyuo lao kareyami.
\v 21 Daniele baa kiŋinya anda dokona yulu pyuo kareyamopa pao Sairose baa yuu Pesa wambunya kiŋi dokome Bapilone pyao nyiya.
\c 2
\s1 Nepukatenesana Kombeya Doko
\p 
\v 1 Ee kana lapo doko Nepukatenesa baa kiŋi kareyamo dokopa baa kombeya mende piya. Dokome baa mona randa malu piyamosa kapa pyuo luu palira ingya naya.
\v 2 Dokona lao banya mali mali sakangepe pipu lengepe nemonga lengepe pepe minyingipi akali dupwame kombeya dokona renge doko polo langyala epena leya. Epapala nakama kiŋinya lenge kambu siyamo dokona roya kareyami.
\v 3 Dokopa kiŋi dokome lao, Namba kombeya mende pipu dokome namba mona randa pilyamo dokona namba renge angi doko apa lao pipu lao selana suu pilyu, leya.
\p 
\v 4 Leyamo dokopa nakamame Arame pii lao isingi lao, Emba kiŋi dokoŋo palu karalu karena. Embena kombeya doko namwa langipi. Dopa pirinyi dokopa namwame renge doko polo langirama, leyami.
\p 
\v 5 Kiŋi dokome doo pipu lenge akali dupwa lamaiyuo, Nakamame kombeya doko akiŋi laope dee renge dokonaŋa laope polo langirami lao suu pyaro karo. Dopa pyuo langya narami ramo nambame nakamana kingi kimbu yongo dupwa pyao suu lao nyuo dee nakamana anda dupwa kokwa sinyi nembo piru lao suu pyao otapu.
\v 6 Dopa pirunupape nakamame kombeya dokona langyuo renge dokoŋo lao polo langirami ramo doko nambame nakama yano pyao bange lapo jero dee nakamana kingi ketae pyambuo lakandaro. Epapu dakepa kombeya doko akiŋi laope dee dokona renge dokope polo langipwape, leya.\fig Danieleme Nepukatenesana kombeya piyamo doko polo lamaiya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="2:3-47"\fig*
\p 
\v 7 Leyamo dokopa pipu lenge akali dupwame kiŋi kando kamba piso soo lao, Embame kombeya doko akiŋi lao langiri ramo doko renge doko polo langirama, leyami.
\p 
\v 8 Dokopa kiŋi dokome pii poraiyuo lao, Nambame pii lapunu doko alowa pii naro doko kandapala nakamame kyambo yuu gii nembo letaminyi doko angi soo nyilyu.
\v 9 Nakamame kombeya dokona langya narami ramo doko nakama peparae randa mendaki dokoko nyerami. Namba suu pingi alowa pipili yaka lao nakamame mona mendaki palyuo namba kyambo langirama lao lao retami. Nakamame kombeya doko akiŋi lao langirami ramo doko nakamame namba kombeyana renge dokoŋo lao langiramilyamo lao soo nyero, leya.
\p 
\v 10 Leyamo dokopa kiŋinya dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso lenge akali dupwame baa isingi lao, Emba selana suu pilini doko yuu muu peparaena mendemepe embena kombeya dokona kapa langya narami. Kiŋi kamame andake mendemepe panda ama porainya renge palenge mendemepe banya akali pipu lengepe nemonga lengepe mali mali sakangepe dupwa kando piso singi pii andake dopale mendepe piso see nange.
\v 11 Emba kiŋi doko. Emba pii andake piso silini dokona mendemepe kapa isingi laa narami ingilyamo. Kapa laa naraminyipa mee bange anatuŋu lao lakandenge dupwame iki kapa langirami. Langiraminyipape nakamame mee wambu role pyao kara nange.
\p 
\v 12 Yuu gii dokopa kiŋi baa imbu singi nyepala yuu Bapilone dokona kiŋi baa dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso lamaiyuo karenge dupwa peparae lapome mange pyakepo pinya laro lao kareya.
\v 13 Pii leyamo doko akali peparaepe dee Danielemoo wane dolosipa pipya peparae rambe rambe palyuo pyaroŋo lao lamaiyuo oteya.
\s1 Anatumi Kombeya Renge Angi Doko Daniele Lasaka Piya
\p 
\v 14 Yanda singi dupwame kiŋi iso karenge dupwana akali mupwa Arioko lenge kareyamo dokona Daniele baa peya. Akali Arioko lenge dokome akali kombeya polo lenge dusipana mange pyakepo pinya leyamisa Daniele baa mona palipala peya.
\v 15 Papala dokopa baame Arioko piso soo lao, Kiŋi dokome akipamo imbu singi nyuo pii dopale doko lapyase? leya. Leyamo dokopa Ariokome dopa piyaŋa lao Daniele lamaiya.
\p 
\v 16 Dokopa Daniele aopa papala baame kiŋi doko kombeya renge angi doko polo langiru lao yuu gii kuki lama mee jinya leya.
\v 17 Lapala dokopa Daniele baa anda papala banya puu minyingi Ananaya Misaele Asarayamoo doo piyamo dupwa polo lamaiya.
\v 18 Yuu Bapilone dokona akali lapo kiŋi doko dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso lenge dupwa pyao kumara dokopa namwa kumwa naramaŋa Anatu yake panda karenge dokome kondome kumuo nyiso kombeya renge angi doko polo langinya lao Anatu piso sokondali pyuo ateŋa lena leya.
\v 19 Enakana yuu gii kukwa dokopa Anatumi renge angi doko Daniele keta pii repa repa pyuo lasaka piyamosa baame Anatu yake panda karenge doko lakandeya.
\q1 
\v 20 Anatu baa soo nyuo angingyuo porainya renge palenge dokome
\q1 banya kingi lakando karalu karamana.
\q1 
\v 21 Baame neta pingipi apu pingipi yuu gii dupwa rapu pingi.
\q1 Baame kiŋi dupwa rombo palyepala dee nyuo isa nembenge.
\q1 Baame akali dupwa soo gisinginya rengepe dee singinya rengepe maingi.
\q1 
\v 22 Mee wambumi see nangepe dee renge yalu piru karengepe dupwa baame panenge.
\q1 Dee baame lapo iminjinginya yalu pyuo singi dupwa soo gisingi.
\q1 Baa keta yanga paupau lao karenge.
\q1 
\v 23 Embame namwa kiŋi doko aki lamairami lao lasaka pyuo
\q1 embame nambana ateŋa dokona isingi yano pyakao
\q1 dee embame namba soo nyinginya rengepe porainya rengepe joo pilini dokona
\q1 nambana rora ambasupi dupwana Anatu nambame emba rape rape lao lakando karo.
\s1 Danieleme Kiŋi Doko Kombeya Piyamo Doko Lamaipala Renge Polo Lamaiya
\p 
\v 24 Akali Arioko lenge dokome kiŋi baame banya dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso lenge akali dupwana mange pyakepo pinya leyamo doko kareyamo dokona Daniele peya. Papala lao, Embame nakama pyao kumaka napipi. Nambame banya kombeya dokona renge doko polo lamairu lao namba minyuo kiŋi petamo dokona paipu, leya.
\p 
\v 25 Dokopa Ariokome aopa Daniele lanyuo kiŋinya lenge kambu dokona papala kiŋi doko lamaiyuo lao, Embame wambu yuu Juta range puu maiyuo nyingi dokona mende kando nyipunu dokome embena kombeya dokona renge aki lao polo langira, leya.
\p 
\v 26 Kiŋi dokome Daniele banya kingi mende Beletesasa lenge doko lamaiyuo, Embame namba kombeya pipu dokonape dee kombeya renge dokonape langirisi? leya.
\p 
\v 27 Dokopa Daniele isingi lao, Emba kiŋi andake, pipu lenge akali mendepe nemonga lenge mendemepe mali mali sakange mendemepe dee akali bui rapu pingi akali dupwana mendemepe emba dokona langirami ingya nalyamo.
\v 28 Dopa piramopape Anatu yake panda karenge dokome kongwalu pii dupwa pano lamaingi. O kiŋi baame emba rengya mende pira lao langipya. Emba luu palipinyi pii repa repa pipi kandapi doko kombeya dakeŋe epapu nambame polo langiruwale.
\p 
\v 29 Emba kiŋi doko luu palipinyipa Anatu renge angi yalu pisi singi dupwa panenge dokome kombeyame rengya pira dupwana lao lasaka pipya.
\v 30 Nambana soo nyingi renge doko andake ingyuo mee akali dupwana suu pingi nyuo isa palyuo pingindena Anatumi renge angi namba lasaka pipyande daa. Emba kiŋi andake doko embena kombeya dokona renge doko soo nyuo dee suu pingi emba keta ipyamo dupwa soo nyuo pelese lao pipya.
\p 
\v 31 Emba kiŋi andake doko. Embena pii repa repa pipinyi dokopa kaname wasisi ama andake wambu yalende yanga paupau lao leya leya pipyamo doko kandalana pakapi.
\v 32 Dokona kyawa doko kana golo keyangeme wasisi dee banya kingi kyangalipi dupwa kana kulingi dokome wasisi dee banya romba lengyarepe dupwa kone kana yalendeme wasisi.
\v 33 Banya kimbu dolapo aneme wasisi dee kimbu kape dolapo paki aneme wasapa dee paki warame wasapa pingi.
\v 34 Emba doko kando palene dokopa kana reeko wambumi minyanda nayaminyi mende maso epapala bange dokona kimbu kape ane warapeme wasisi doko piyamosa poro lao muu muu piya.
\v 35 Yuu gii mendaki dokopa anepe warape bange kone kana yalepe kana kulingipi dee kana golope poro lao muu muu pipala panyi pilyamopa sinjimu singi dopale ingiya. Dopa piyamo dokopa poraiye dokome kuki mendepe pyarepala paa nana lao soo peya. Dopa piyamopape kana doko ando yuu kyau ingyuo andakyapala yuu muu dupwa peparae minyarambu nyiya.
\p 
\v 36 Doko embena kombeya dokoŋo. Epapu nambame kiŋi andake doko renge angi doko polo langiruwale.
\v 37 Emba kiŋi andake doko. Kiŋi menge dupwana emba iki mupwa. Anatu yake panda karenge dokome emba kiŋi rombo palyuo porainya renge joo wambu wakale dupwame emba kando rape rape lao lakando karena leya.
\v 38 Dokona mena suwape yakape peparae dee wambu yuu muunya palaminyi dupwape emba mupwa ingyuo iso karare lao wasiya. Emba kyawa kana golome wasisi doko dopale karene.
\v 39 Emba kiŋi karaparene dokopa dee kiŋi mendeko karara. Doko emba karene dopa pyuo andake ingyuo kara nara. Dee doko soo paparamo dokopa repo pyuo kiŋi mendeko dokome yuu muu dupwa peparae iso karara. Baa kone kana wasisi yale karara.
\v 40 Dokopa enakana kiŋi kisima ingyuo doko ama porai ane dopale ingyuo karara. Ane dokome isa palipala bange lapo pyao injo muu muu pingi doko suu pyao kiŋi dokome kiŋi wamba karenge dupwa pyao nembalu nembo nembara.
\v 41 Kimbu kapepe pambupi aneme pakiki wasisi dee paki warame wasisi kandee kande. Renge doko kiŋinya isingi yulu dupwa liti pyuo wakale wakale sera. Ane doko wara dokopa pyasiyamo dokona anena porainya renge mende palamo lao sera.
\v 42 Doko kimbu pambu paki ane dee paki wara dokona suu pyao renge doko kiŋinya isingi yulu dokona lapo porai ingyuo dee lapo mee manda rao isa para.
\v 43 Embame ane doko wara dokopa kiminjiyamo kandeko doko suu pyao doko kiŋinya isingi dokona akali mupwa dupwame nakamana ree palu nyuo pyasimwali lao mendena wanenge doko yango mendali maiyuo pilya pena pirami. Dopa piraminyipape ane doko wara dokopa kapa pyasa nangenyili pyuo nakama kapa pii narami.
\v 44 Yuu gii kiŋi dusipame iso kararaminyi dokopa Anatu yake panda karenge dokome kiŋi enenge mende rombo palyuo baa mee karalu karena lara. Kiŋi wakale dupwame baa pyao anamasi minya narami. Dopa piramopape baame kiŋi doloma peparae pyao isa palyapala baa mee iso palyuo puu para.
\v 45 Embame kandene dokopa kana mende yuu kyau dokona pisapala mendeme minyanda nayaminyipa rangeme lukundo epapala anepe kone kanape warape kana kulingipi dee golopeme wasisi bange wambu yale piyamo kandee kande. Anatu Kamame Andake Wakasa dokome rengya mende pira dokona emba kiŋi andake doko lasaka pilyamo. Nambame kombeya angi emba pipinyili pyuo langilyu dee dokona renge angi kinyi rolae dusipa langyuo pilyu, leya Danieleme.
\s1 Kiŋi Dokome Isingi Yano Pyao Daniele Bange Lapo Maiya
\p 
\v 46 Doko kiŋi Nepukatenesame Danielena lenge kambu siyamo dokona wapambu pii pyao pangu sepala baa bange lapo maiyuo dee rendamu pingi kiso maiyuo pimana lao wambu dupwa lamaiya.
\v 47 Embame nambana kombeyana renge angi dokona polo langipinyi dokona embena Anatu doko kamame andake wakasa mee bange anatu dupwa nyuo isa palyuo baa Kamongo kiŋi dupwana baa ketae ingyuo karenge dee baameko kombeya renge angi dupwa panenge doko soo nyilyu, leya.
\v 48 Lapala baame Daniele yulu andake maiyuo yuu Bapilone doko iso karena lao dee akali lapo kiŋi doko yulu dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso karenge dupwana baa mupwa ingyuo karo pinya lapala bange keyange dupwa maiya.
\v 49 Danieleme mende piso siyamuli pyuo kiŋi dokome Setarakemoo Mesakemoo Apenekomoo dusipa yuu Bapilone dokona yulu wakale wakale singi dupwa rapu pyuo karena leya. Leyamo dokopa Daniele baa yuu Bapilone kiŋinya anda dokona yulu pyuo kareya.
\c 3
\s1 Wambu Yalende Kana Golome Wasisi Doko Kiŋi Nepukatenesame Wambu Dupwa Lakandena Lao Mana Lamaiya
\p 
\v 1 Kiŋi Nepukatenesame wambu yale kana golome banya akali dupwame wasinya leyamo doko ama londe mita akalisa lama ipisu yanda ipingi dee ama andake doko mita rema dopale ingiya. Wasapala yuu lama lama kingi Dura lenge yuu Bapilone singi dokona pisinya leya.
\v 2 Lapala dokopa banya akali mupwape isingi akali dupwape kana isingi dupwape kote singi dupwape gapomane mupwa dupwape gapomane kukipi dee akali mupwa dupwa peparae yuu liti dokona range dupwape nyuo pyaso malu palyinya leya. Kiŋi Nepukatenesame mee bange wambu yale kana golome wasapala ketae pisiyamo dokona nakama lakando ketae pyambwakala epena leya.
\v 3 Dokopa akali mupwa dupwa peparae epo wambu yale bange doko ketae pyambwarami lao nyuo malu palyapala wambu yale bange dokona lenge kambu siyamo dokona kareyami.
\v 4 Dokopa kiŋinya pii polo lenge akali dokome pii poraiyuo ketae palyuo lao,
\v 5 Akali yuu muu dupwana range peparaepe pii wakale wakale lenge dupwape, Nakama bikuli laraminyi pii doko sepala dee musiki rara wakale wakale laraminyi pii dupwa soo pipala aopa kiŋi Nepukatenesame wambu yale kana golome wasisi pisiyamo doko wapambu pii pyao pangu sepala lakandarami ingilyamo.
\v 6 Wambu mendeme pangu sepala lakanda naramo doko waiya lao isare ama alyu rao karenge dokona sukusa pyambwarami, leya.
\v 7 Dokona lao akali yuu muu wakale wakale rangepe pii wakale wakale lengepe dupwa peparaeme musiki doloma pii leyamo dokopa aopa pangu sepala mee bange wambu yale kana golome wasisi kiŋi Nepukatenesame pisiyamo doko lakandeyami.
\s1 Juu Akali Rema Kando Nakama Kamba Letaminyi Leyami
\p 
\v 8 Dokopa Bapilone akali lapo akali kiŋi kareyamo dokona epapala Juu akali dusipana lao yango palyuo isa palyamwali lao leyami.
\v 9 Nakamame kiŋi Nepukatenesa kando lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko palu karalu karare, leyami.
\v 10 Emba kiŋi andake doko, musiki kanda soo laramopa wambu peparae aopa pangu sepala mee bange wambu yale kana golome wasisi doko lakandapengele.
\v 11 Dee wambu mendeme pangu soo lakanda nara ramo doko isare ama alyu uliyapu nyuo rao karenge dokona sukusa pyambwarami lapi kandape.
\v 12 Juu akali lapo Setarakemoo Mesake Apenekomoo yuu Bapilone dokona mupwa ingyuo karena lao rombo palyii kande dupwame emba kiŋi andake dokome mawa pii lapinyi doko warombo see nalyaminyi. Nakamame embena mee bange anatuŋu lenge doko lakanda nao dee wambu yale kana golome wasisi pisinyi doko kando pangu soo lakanda nalyaminyiko.
\p 
\v 13 Yuu gii dokopa kiŋi doko baa ama wakasa imbwuapala akali rema dusipa baa peteyamo dokona minyuo epena leya.
\v 14 Lapala baame nakama lamaiyuo lao, Setarake Mesake Apeneko nakamame nambana mee bange wambu yale kana golome wasisi pisiyunu doko kando pangu soo lakanda nao dee nambana mee bange anatuŋu lenge doko lakandaka nao pimi. Doko kinyisi?
\v 15 Epapu dakepa bikuli piipi musiki wakale wakale piipi laramo sepala dokopa aopa nakama pangu soo wambu yale kana golome wasisi doko lakandalapape. Daaŋa lapala nakama dopa pii narami ramo doko aopa dokopako ane isame kame pisi panda sukusa isare alyu uliyapu nyuo rao karenge dokona sukusa pyambwarami. Dokopa anatu mendeme nakama lete nyeraŋa lao suu pilyamisi? leya.
\p 
\v 16 Dopa leyamo dokopa Setarake Mesake Apenekomoome isingi lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko, namwa rangena lao yanda pyuo isingi mende laa narama.
\v 17 Anatu namwa yulu pyakamilyamano dokome doo isare alyu uliyapu nyingipi sukusa dokonape dee embena porai renge dokonape mee kapa pyuo kyawa lete nyero lara ramo kapa lete nyera.
\v 18 Baame kamame namwa lete nyii naramopape namwa emba kiŋi doko soo lape. Namwame embena mee bange antuŋu lenge doko lakanda narama dee wambu yale kana golome wasisi pisinyi doko pangu soo lakandaka naramako, leyami.
\s1 Juu Akali Dusipa Isare Dokona Pyambuyami
\p 
\v 19 Dokopa Setarake Mesake Apenekomoo kando kiŋi Nepukatenesa baa ama lenge kambu poro imbu manjo wakasa imbwaya. Imbwuapala banya akali dupwa lamaiyuo isare doko ama andake ingyuo rena leŋe yuu yanda ipingi ingyuo isa pyambuo kisinya leya.
\v 20 Banya yanda singi ami akali porai dupwame lamaiyuo akali rema dusipa puu pyapala isare alyu uliyapu nyingi dokona pyambunya leya.
\v 21 Dokona lao nakamame nakamana komau piyaminyi dupwa mee wapuro kareyaminyipa puu pyapala isare alyu uliyapu nyingi sukusa dokona pyambuyami.
\v 22 Dokopa kiŋi doko pii lao isare doko ama wakasa rao alyinya leyamosa isare ulingi dupwame akali lanyuo pyao pyambwala peyami dupwa rao kumuyami.
\v 23 Dokona lao wane Setarake Mesake Apenekomoo dusipa puu pyaro karo isa rao ulikasi nyuo kareyamo anda suku dokona pyambuyamisa lukundaro pao paleyami.
\p 
\v 24 Dokopa Nepukatenesame banya petenge isa dokona piso pyakao epapala mona nembaoko banya akali mupwa dupwa piso soo lao, Namwame akali rema dusipa puu pyapala isare sukusa dokona pyambwa namwase? leya.
\p Nakamame isingi lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko. Waa, namwame pyambwamwa, leyami.\fig Akali kisima doko baa anatu yalende karamo.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="3:25"\fig*
\p 
\v 25 Doko dee akipamo nambame akali kisima isare dokona kata papyuo karaminyi kandelyose? lao piso siya. Nakama puu pyaro kara nami dee isare dokome nakama raope pii napya. Dokona akali kisima doko baa anatu yalende karamo, leya.
\s1 Juu Akali Dusipa Nyisa Nyepala Yulu Andake Maiya
\p 
\v 26 Kiŋi Nepukatenesa baa isare alyu uliyapu nyuo rao karenge dokona kambu dokona papala nakama kee lao, Setarake, Mesake, Apeneko, Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokona kendemande akali dusipa nyisa ipupwa, leya. Leyamo dokopa nakama aopa nyisa epeyami.
\v 27 Dokopa gapomane mupwape gapomane kuki dupwape dee kiŋinya akali mupwape nyuo pyasapala akali isarena randa nyuo raa nayaminyi dusipa kandala epeyami. Nakamana kyawasi dusipana pinjingisape mende raa nayami. Nakamana komau dupwana mende raa nayamo dee nakamana yongo dupwana isare sukwa ai pyuope pii naya.
\p 
\v 28 Dokopa kiŋi dokome lao, Setarake Mesake Apenekomoona Anatu doko lakandamana. Baame banya aŋala doko peyapala akali baa keta pyamalyuo mona maiyuo karo banya yulu pyakamingi dasipa kyawa lete nyipyalyamo. Nakamame nambana pii lapunu dokona warombo see napala nakama range randa nyisasaramano lao paka napala mee bange anatuŋu lenge lapo pangu sepala lakandenge kandale doko suu pyao nakama rangena doko iki lakandeyami.
\p 
\v 29 Dokona epapu namba mawa pii palyuo leto, leya. Yuu muu peparae dupwana wambu mendemepe dee pii rara wakale wakale lenge dupwana mendemepe Setarake Mesakemoo Apenekomoona Anatu dokona kingi doko nyuo isa palyaramo wambu doko banya kimbu kingipi pyao suu lanyi nembo banya anda doko yuu sinjimupi manjomomo nao para. Nakamana Anatu nyiso lete nyipyamo dopale mendepe kara nange.
\p 
\v 30 Yuu Bapilone dokona wane Setarake Mesake Apenekomoo dusipa wambo yulu pyuo karengenepape kiŋi dokome yulu ulipili andake ingyuo maiya.
\c 4
\s1 Kiŋi Nepukatenesame Kombeya Lapo Ingyuo Piya
\p 
\v 1 Yuu muu peparaena wambu palengepe dee rara wakale wakalepe dee wambu pii wakale wakale lengepe dupwa peparae kiŋi Nepukatenesame wai nembo nakama peparae, Yako leto, leya.
\v 2 Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa yake panda karenge dokome yulu wambumi kando yamarangungipi yulu andake wambumi pii nangendepe namba keta pyuo lasaka pipyamo doko nakama langiruwale, selapape.
\q1 
\v 3 Anatumi yulu andake wambumi kando yamarangungi dupwa pyuo lasaka pingi.
\q1 Baame yulu porai wambumi pii nange dupwa pingi.
\q1 Anatu doko baa kiŋi dokome yuu gii peparae iso karo puu para.
\p 
\v 4 Namba Nepukatenesa bange malu retapunu dupwana range rae maiyuo nambana anda dokona waa lao kapa palipu.
\v 5 Dopa pipunupape namba luu palipunu dokopa kombeya paka pingi mende pipala pii repa repa pyuo kandapala pakame kumapu.
\v 6 Dokona lao kombeya renge dokona nakamame langiramiŋi lapala nambame yuu Bapilone dokona kiŋinya akali lapo yulu dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso lenge dupwa namba pisipu dokona lanyuo epena lapu.
\v 7 Dokopa mali mali sakangepe nemonga lengepe pipu lengepe dee bui kandaro karo apa pirase lao karengepe dupwa peparae lanyuo imi. Iminyipa nambana kombeya angi piyunu doko lamaipu. Lamaipunupape nakamame renge angi doko polo langya nami.
\v 8 Dokopa Daniele baa enakana andakare ipya. (Banya kingi mende doko Beletesasa lenge. Doko nambana anatuŋu lao kingi lenge doko.) Anatu Poo Pyasi dokona imambu doko baa keta paleyamo dokome kombeya angi pipunu doko nambame baa lamaipu.
\v 9 Nambame baa kando lao, Beletesasa, akali mali mali sakange dupwana mupwa doko Anatu Poo Pyasi dokona imambu doko emba keta karamo doko namba emba silyu. Dokona emba kongwalu pii peparae dupwana emba silini dokona nambana kombeya pipunu doko dakeŋe. Renge aki lao namba langipi, leyo.
\p 
\v 10 Namba luu palipunu dokopa yuu muu peparaena anda suku dokona isa ama londe mende karapyamo pii repa repa pyuo kandapu.
\v 11 Doko ando kameyako ingyuo kamame ando ama londe ingyapala yake dulu kando nyipyamo dokopa yuu muu dupwana wambu peparaeme kandarami ingyapya.
\v 12 Banya isa yokonge dupwa ama keyange wakasa dee jingi dupwa lyuo kui lao epenge dupwa yuu muu peparaena wambu karenge dupwa kapa lyuo narami ingingi. Dee mena rae lenge dupwa isa renge rau lenge dokona imambu soo karengepya dee yaka dupwa banya wangya dupwana anda pingipya. Dee bange lete karenge dupwa peparaeme banya jingi doko lyuo nengeko.
\p 
\v 13 Namba pii repa repa dokona lao suu pyao palipunu dokopa aŋala yuu peparae iso karenge mende yake panda piso isa ipyamo doko kandapu.
\v 14 Epapala baame pii poraiyuo lao, Isa doko poko isa palyapala wangya pangepe dupwa muu muu pepe. Dee isa yokonge dupwa loo lapala jingi dupwa yuu wakale wakale dupwana pyao nembape. Nembapala mena isa palu silyaminyi dupwa ralinyi nembo dee banya wangya dokona yaka petaminyi dupwa ralinyi nembo pipi, lapya.
\v 15 Dopa pirinyipape ane puu dokome dee kone kana puu dokomepe isa sinju doko awali lao puu pyanyi palyapala kaeyape. Yuu dokona rambi pipya petena kaeyare.
\p Epapu akali dake keta pipyae dupwa kondo petena dee baa mena rarape dee ee nenge rarape dupwana pipya role pyapeta palena.
\v 16 Ee kana yanda ipingi nyepo baa keta wambunya suu pingi doko pali nara. Baa keta menana suu pingi palira.
\v 17 Dake aŋala iso karalu karenge dupwana pii lalu lao lao palyimi doko. Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokona porai renge dokome mee akali kiŋi dupwana isingi yulu doko nyuo isa palyingi. Baame range maso akali mende kiŋi inginyi pyambuo rombo palyingi. Akali kamame kuki karelyaminyipape baame mende rombo palyilyamo doko kiŋi wasingi. Dokona lao pii doko wambu peparae sinya, lapya.
\p 
\v 18 Kiŋi Nepukatenesame lao, Kombeya doko namba pipuŋu. Beletasasa epapu renge doko aki lao langipi. Nambana akali angi dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso lenge dupwame langi naminyipape emba doo Anatu Poo Pyasi dokona imambu doko emba keta karapyamo dokome embame kapa langiri ingilyamo, leya.\fig Isa kamame ando ama londe doko yake dulu kando nyipya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="4:20"\fig*
\s1 Danieleme Kombeya Dokona Renge Doko Polo Lamaiya
\p 
\v 19 Daniele banya kingi mende Beletesasa lenge dokome kombeya dokona lao sepala mona randame kumuo baa mende lara ingya naya. Dopa piyamosa kiŋi dokome lao, Beletesasa, emba kombeya dokomepe dee dokona renge dokomepe emba mona randanyi pyambunya laa napipi, leya.
\p Leyamo dokopa Beletesasame isingi lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko, kombeya dokope dee dokona renge angi epara dokope emba keta pali nao embena nyisu petenge dupwa keta palipyali doko kapa ingyapyali, leya.
\v 20 Isa kamame ando ama londe doko yake dulu kando nyipyamo dokopa yuu muu dupwana wambu peparaeme kandarami ingyapya.
\v 21 Banya yoko dupwa ama keyange ingyapala dee banya jingi lyingi kapa lyepala yuu muu peparaena wambu dupwa kapa lyuo narami ingyapya. Dee mena suwa rae lenge dupwa isa renge rau lenge dokona imambu soo karami dee banya wangya dokona yaka dupwa anda pimi leya.
\p 
\v 22 Emba kiŋi andake doko. Emba isa dopale. Emba ama londe porai wakasa. Emba ando ama andake ingyapala yake kando nyepala embena porainya renge dokome yuu muu dusipa peparae iso karenge.
\v 23 Emba kiŋi andake dokome kando karapinyi dokopa aŋala mende yake panda piso epo lapya. Isa doko pokanyi isa palyapala dokopa kokwa soo nembena lapya. Dopa pirinyipape isa sinju doko yuu dokona petena kaeyare. Kaepala renge dokona ane puu dokomepe dee kone kana puu dokomepe awali lao puu pyapala yuu dokona rambi pipya petena kaeyare. Dopa pipala akali dake keta pipyae dupwa kondo petena dee ee kana yanda ipingi nyepo baa mena dupwa pipya palyuo karena lapya leya.
\p 
\v 24 Emba kiŋi andake doko. Dake renge angi doko. Dake Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokome emba keta piraŋa lao leyamo doko.
\v 25 Emba wambu menge dupwa pipya rekya lao nyisa papala mena suwa rae lengepe pipya palyuo kararami. Dee emba mena bulamakao yale okese lenge rambi nenge dopale ingyuo nao ee kana yanda ipingi kamanda palyuo kararenepa pipyae dupwa kondo epo emba keta piso karara. Dokopa embame lao, Mee isa wambunya kiŋinya isingi yulu dupwa peparae Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokome rolo rapu pyuo karenge. Baame yuu dupwana kiŋi karena lao rombo palyingi lare, leya.
\v 26 Aŋala dupwame isa sinju doko mee yuu dokona petena lao pii leya. Dokona renge angi doko embame Anatumi yuu muu dupwa peparae rolo rapu pyuo karenge lao larene dokopa emba dee kamba range kiŋi karare.
\v 27 Dokona lao Emba kiŋi andake doko. Namba dopa pii dapa pii leto dupwa moko minyuo piri. Koo pilini dupwa yaki nyuo kaepala yulu keyange pyuo wambu pendewa dupwa sakame kumuo nyisare. Dopa pirinyi dokopa emba dee kapa palyuo karare, leya.
\p 
\v 28 Leyamuli pyuo yulu dusipa peparae kiŋi Nepukatenesa baa keta piya.
\v 29 Kana akalisa ipisu lama iki papeyamo dokopa yuu Bapilone doko banya kiŋinya anda yangi ketae dokona kata papyuo kareya.
\v 30 Karapala baame lao, kanda. Yuu Bapilone andake doko. Nambana taone mupwa dokome nambana porainya rengepe yanga paupau lenge rengepe neta rengepe dupwa lasaka pipuli lao piyu, leya.
\p 
\v 31 Pii doko ene banya nenge kata dokona potemo lalana piyamo dokopa yake panda piso pii mende epo lao, Kiŋi Nepukatenesa, nambame pii leto dake sepe. Epapu embena kiŋinya isingi yulu doko emba keta kingi raka lao nyisa pelyamo.
\v 32 Dokopa emba mee wambu dupwa palaminyi dokona dopale ingyuo pali napala nyisa pao mena suwa rae lenge pipya palu kararami. Dee mena bulamakao yale okese lenge rambi nenge dopale ingyuo rambi dupwa nao palu kararenepa ee kana yanda ipingi nyepo dusipa epo para. Dokopa embame polo lao Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokome banya porainya renge dokome mee isa akali kiŋinya isingi yulu dupwa rapu pyuo karenge dee baame yuu dupwana akali mende kiŋi karena lao rombo palyingi lare, leya.
\p 
\v 33 Pii doo leyamo dusipa aopa pyaka siya. Dokopa kiŋi Nepukatenesa baa wambu pipya role pyao pali napala nyisa pao mena suwa rae lenge pipya palyuo karo pyuo mena okese rambi nenge dopale ingyuo dokona nao palyuo kareya. Dokopa pipyae dupwa kondo pao baa keta piso kareya. Dee banya kyawa dupwa ando londapala yaka kambe imanji yale ingiya. Dee banya kinjipa dupwa epo kyanga ingyapala yaka kinjipa ingiya.
\s1 Nepukatenesame Anatu Lakandeya
\p 
\v 34 Kiŋi dokome lao, Ee kana yanda ipingi nyepo papeyamo dokopa yake dulu kandalyuo kandeyo. Kandapala suu pingi wambu kopyali minyuo suu pyao kareyo doko kaepala Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa karenge doko ketae pyambuo rape rape lao lakandeyo.
\q1 Baame iso rapu pyuo karalu karara.
\q1 Banya isingi yulu doko yuu gii peparae soo puu para.
\q1 
\v 35 Wambu isa yuu dakena palaminyi dupwa angi mende daaŋa lao kandanyi nembelyamo.
\q1 Aŋala yake panda dokona karenge dupwape wambu isa yunya palaminyi dupwape baa isarena karaminyi.
\q1 Mendemepe banya yulu pilyamo dupwana yango palya nao
\q1 dee baame yulu aki pilyamo dupwa piso see narami ingilyamo,
\m leya.
\p 
\v 36 Nambana suu pingi keyange rolae doko range epo paleyamo dokopa nambana kingi andake lenge dokope wambu yuupi iso karenge yulu dokope dee nambana isa yulunya neta rengepe namba range keta jiya. Dokopa nambana yulu pingi akali lapope dee akali mupwa ingyuo karenge dupwape namba yako lao nyepala kiŋinya porainya renge joo wambumi namba wamba lakandengenepape epapu kamame ulipili pyambuo rape rape lao lakandeyami.
\p 
\v 37 Dokona epapu namba Nepukatenesame, Yake Pandana Kiŋi doko kingi ketae pyambuo rape rape lao lakandelyo. Renge doko yulu peparae baa keyangeko pingi. Baa yuu peparae rolaeko pyuo karo wambu mendali kamame ulipili mupwa lao suu pingi dupwa nyuo kui lao kuki ingyuo inyimungu karena lao pingi, leya.
\c 5
\s1 Belesasana Pati Andake Lao Nenge Kisiya
\p 
\v 1 Belesasa baa kiŋi ingyuo kareyamo gii dokopa pati andake lao nenge kisapala akali mupwa taosande mendaki (1,000) epena lao nakama role pyao piso ipwa waene neyami.
\v 2 Nakama ipwa nao peteyaminyi dokopa Belesasame lamaiyuo, Kana golo kana kulingipimi wasisi kapope pere warakepe Jerusaleme tembole anda dokona siyamo banya rakange Nepukatenesame nyuo minyuo epeyamo dupwa minyuo epena leya. Kiŋi dokome baape banya akali mupwa dupwape banya etengepe dee enda konda pyuo nyingipi ipwa dokona kyano pyuo naramaŋa lao nyepala epena leya.
\v 3 Leyamo yuu gii mendaki dokopa pere warakepe kapope dupwa nyuo minyuo epeyaminyipa dupwana ipwa waene kyano pyuo nyuo neyami.
\v 4 Napala mee bange anatu kana golope kana kulingipi kone kanape anepe isape dee mee kanapeme wasisi dupwa lakandeyami.\fig Wambu kinginde epo maro lapala pepa piya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="5:5"\fig*
\p 
\v 5 Dokopa aopa kiŋinya anda dokona kana semene apya isare lambe reyamo dokona yanga paupau leyamo dorena ingyuo wambu kinginde epo maro lapala pepa piya. Doo pepa piyamo dokopa kiŋi dokome kingi doko kandeya.
\v 6 Dokopa baa yongo nembo pakame kumuo banya kimbu dupwa walu walu leya.
\v 7 Dopa pipala baa pii porai lao wambu mendeme pipu lenge akalipi nemonga lenge akalipi bui isingi ene rengya mende pira lao lenge akali dupwape nyela pena leya. Nakama epeyaminyi dokopa kiŋi dokome lamaiyuo lao, Mendeme pepa doko yaka lapala renge dokona aki lao langiramo wambu doko komau muku londe mende wapupala dee kana golo kii puu banya mange dokona soo piramo doko kandapala wambu dupwame baa lakandarami. Dokopa baa kiŋinya isingi yulu porai dokona repo ingyuo pisira.
\v 8 Dokopa kiŋinya akali dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso lenge dupwa peparae repeta epeyami. Epeyaminyipape pepa doko laope panda renge dokonape mende lamairami ingya naya.
\v 9 Dokona lao kiŋi Belesasa baa mona randame kumapala ama yongo nembeyamo dokopa banya akali mupwa dupwa mende aki pirama lao see nayami.
\p 
\v 10 Dokopa kiŋipi banya akali mupwape dupwana leyaminyi doko sepala enda kuini baa nenge nao petenge panda dokona konando peya. Papala baame lao, Emba kiŋi andake palu karalu karare. Emba mona randame kumuo embena yongo nemba napipi, leya.
\v 11 Embena kiŋinya isingi panda dokona akali mende Anatu Poo Pyasi dokona imambu doko palengende karamo. Wamba embena rakane kiŋi kareyamo dokopa akali doko kyawa sisingi keyange palenge rengepe singinya rengepe soo nyinginya renge mee bange anatunya soo nyinginya renge dopalepe baa keta paleyamo lasaka piya. Dopa piyamosa kiŋi Nepukatenesa embena rakane dokome doo pipu lenge akalipi nemonga lengepe mali mali sakangepe dee bui isingi ene mende pira dokona polo lengepe dupwana baa mupwa ingyuo karena lao rombo palyiya.
\v 12 Akali doko baa menge dupwa isa palyili lao ama mora piso kombeya rengepe kongwalu pii dupwana angi rengepe pii yalu pyuo lenge dupwana rengepe polo lao baa mona angi palyuo soo nyuo karenge. Dokona lao akali Daniele kiŋi dokome kingi mende Beletesasa leyamo doko nyela pena lape. Epapala dokopa renge angi dupwana peparae polo langira, leya.
\s1 Danieleme Pepa Pyasi Dokona Polo Lamaiya
\p 
\v 13 Dokopa aopa Daniele baa minyuo kiŋinya lenge kambu dokona peyami. Dokopa kiŋi dokome kando lao, Emba Danielese? Nambana rakane kiŋi dokome Juta piso, Emba Juu akali karapusi ingyuo minyuo epeya dokose? lao piso siya.
\v 14 Anatu Poo Pyasinya imambu doko emba keta palipyasa mora piso singinya rengepe soo nyinginya rengepe emba keta palamo laminyi doko namba sipu.
\v 15 Doko pipu lenge akalipi dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso lenge akalipi dupwa minyuo epo pepa pyasi dake yaka lao renge dokona namba langinya lapu. Dopa lapunupape nakamame renge angi dokona polo langya nami.
\v 16 Dokona embame kongwalu pii dupwanape dee pii yalu pyuo suu pingi dupwanape koto nyuo dee renge angi dupwa embame polo lenge laminyi doko epapu namba sipu. Dokona embame pepa dake yaka lapala renge polo langiri ramo doko emba komau muku londe mende wapuri. Emba akali mupwaŋa lao wambumi serami lao kana golome wasisi kii puu doko embena mange dokona awali lao sere. Dopa pipala emba kiŋinya isingi yulu dokona repo ingyuo karare, leya.
\p 
\v 17 Leyamo dokopa Danieleme isingi lao, Embena bange jelana letene dupwa range reto panda wambu wakale lapo mairi. Dokopa nambame kiŋi andake doko pepa dokona palipyamo doko yaka lapala renge angi dokona aki lao doko polo langiru, leya.
\p 
\v 18 Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokome embena rakane Nepukatenesa doko kiŋi ingyuo waso banya kingi ketae pyambuo yulu andake maiya.
\v 19 Baa ama akali andake dokome wambu yuu muu dupwana peparaemepe wambu rara dupwamepe pii wakale wakale lenge dupwamepe baa kando pakapala walu walu lao karenge. Baame wambu mendali pyao kumapulinya suu pingi ramo doko pyao kumakapalako kaenge. Dee wambu mendali lete pena lao suu pingi ramo doko lete pena kaenge. Baame wambu mendali lakandanyi pyambuo rape rape laope panda elyanyi pyambuope pinya suu pingi doko pipala kaenge.
\v 20 Dopa pinginyipape baa mona kana pokapala range mupwa lao suu pyao wambu menge dupwa mona randanyi pyambungi dokome banya kiŋinya yulu doko yaki nyuo kaepala wambu dupwame baa rape rape lao kara nayaminyipa baa isa peya.
\v 21 Baa wambu palenge raka dokona pali napala nyisa papala banya suu pingi doko menana dopale ingyuo paleya. Baa mena donge rae lenge dupwa pipya palu karapala mena bulamakao yale okese lenge rambi nenge dopale ingyuo neya. Dee baa pipyae dupwana mende yambe pyaa nao kamanda mee wau kanya dupwana langa palu karo piya. Dopa pipala Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokome mee akalinya kiŋi yulu dupwa iso karo wambu mende baame rombo palyingi doko maingi lao baa soo gisiya.
\p 
\v 22 Dupwa peparae sipinyipape emba banya ikinyingi doko range kuki ingyuo inyimungu kara nalene.
\v 23 Dopa pipala emba Anatu yake panda karenge dokopa kamba lapala banya tembole anda dokona pee kapo pere warakepe singi dupwa nyepala minyuo epee kande. Dopa pyuo epapala embape embena akali mupwa dupwape embena etene dupwape dee enda lapo mee konda pyuo nyingi peteyami. Pisipala dupwa pipya kapo dupwana ipwa waene kyano pyuo nao role pyao kana golope kana kulingipi kone kanape anepe isape mee kanape dupwame mee bange anatu wambu kanda nangepe dee pii see nangepe dee mende maso suu pyaa nangepe dupwa waso lakandeyami. Dopa piminyipape emba kumarene dupwanape lete karare dupwanape rolo dee emba yulu peparae pilini dupwana iso karo pilyamo Anatu doko embame rape rape lao ketae pyambuo lakanda nalene.
\v 24 Renge dokona pepa pii dusipa pinya lao Anatumi kingi doko peeyapya.
\p 
\v 25 Dopa lao pepa angi doko pyasi paleya. Yaka lengepe, yaka lengepe, sikyali pyuo kenda pingipi, liti pingipi, pii dupwa pyasi paleya.
\v 26 Epapu renge angi doko dake. Yaka lengena renge doko. Embena kiŋinya isingi yuu gii dusipa Anatumi yaka lao karapala ote pinya nembara.
\v 27 Kenda pingi dokona renge doko, Emba sikyali mendena makande pyuo kandeyamo dokopa ama kaka yau yaepa ingiya.
\v 28 Liti pingi dokona renge dake. Embena kiŋinya isingi panda dusipa wakale wakale pyuo liti pipala Mitia wambu maiyuo dee Pesa wambu maiyuo pira ingiya, Danieleme leya.
\p 
\v 29 Yuu gii dokopako aopa Belesasame Daniele komau muku londe mende wapakamyuo baa akali mupwaŋa lao wambumi serami lao kana golome wasisi kii puu doko banya mange dokona sakamyuo pinya leya. Dopa pipala baa kiŋinya isingi yulu dokona repo ingyuo petena lao wasiya.
\v 30 Yuu gii kukwa mendaki dokopako Belesasa yuu Bapilone kiŋi doko pyao kumakayami.
\v 31 Dokopa akali Darisi lenge yuu Mitia range dokome ee kana akalisa pakinyamange ipisu lama (62) nembo karapala kiŋinya panda nyiya.
\c 6
\s1 Daniele Baa Mena Laene Palenge Yuwale Reeko Dokona Paleya
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa banya yuu liti isingi dusipana mupwa ingyuo iso kararami lao Darisimi gapomane akali andete mendaki dee akalisa lama (120) rombo palyiya.
\v 2 Palyapala banya bange dupwape dee gapomane akali dupwape isinya lao Daniele baape akali lama dolapope rombo palyiya.
\v 3 Dokopa Danieleme gapomane akali dupwape yulu isingi akali dolapope nyuo isa palyuo baa yulu kamame keyange ingyuo pinya piya. Baa ama mondo koo lao pinya piyamosa kiŋi dokome banya isingi yuu peparaena Daniele baa mupwa ingyuo karapyali lao suu piya.
\v 4 Dopa piyamosa akali yango yulu iso karenge dolapomepe dee gapomane dupwamepe Danieleme kiŋinya yuu iso karo yulu piyamo dokona aki koo mende pilyamo lao kando koto kareyami. Dopa piyaminyipape Daniele baa rape rape lao yulu angi kinyi keyange dokonako pipala yulu koope kopetamepe mende pii naya dokome baa aki koo mende pilyamo lao kotalana saka nayami.
\v 5 Dopa pipala nakama range lao dopa leyami. Namwame Daniele baa yulu mendena koo pingi lao koto nyii naramalyamo. Dopa piramopape baa misi yulu pilyamo dokona iki koo mende kando nyerama, leyami.
\p 
\v 6 Dopa lapala nakama kiŋi kandala peyami. Papala dopa lao, Kiŋi Darisi, emba kiŋi andake palu karalu karare, leyami.
\v 7 Namwa peparae embena yulu isoko kando karenge dupwa yulu rapu pingipi gapomanepe gapomane kuki dupwape dee yulu wakale pingi dupwapeme lao palyamwa doko emba kiŋi andake dokome lowa porai mende lao wasapala alowa pii nao minyaro karalu karare. Mawa pii pyao reto yuu gii akalisa rema (30) dusipana mendemepe mee bange anatuŋu lao lakandenge lapope akali lapope bange jinya lao piso see nana. Emba kiŋi andake dokona iki keta piso sinya lare. Larenepa mendeme pii doko warombo see nara ramo doko mena laene palenge yuwale dokona pyambware, leyami.
\v 8 Emba kiŋi andake doko mawa pii dake pyao palyuo pepa dokona embena kingi pyao palyape. Dokopa dokona palu paliramopa yuu Mitia dee yuu Pesape dolapona lowa pyasi palenge dupwa alowa pii nangenyili pyuo mee pyasi palira.
\v 9 Dokopa kiŋi Darisimi mawa pii leyamo doko pyao retapala banya kingi isarena piya.
\v 10 Mawa pii doo pyao palyami leyaminyi doko Daniele sepala banya anda peya. Banya anda dokona ketae dulurename panda singi dokona windowa lapo Jerusaleme kanda kanda singi. Dokona baa yuu peparae pinginyili pyuo windowa lumbwapala wapambu pii pyaro piso yuu gii mendakinya yuu remasa lao Anatu ateŋa leya.\fig Windowa lumbwapala wapambu pii pyaro piso ateŋa leya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="6:10"\fig*
\p 
\v 11 Dokopa akali dusipa Danieleme Anatu kando ateŋa leyamo dokopa epo kando kareyami.
\v 12 Karapala peparae nyuo pyasapala Danieleme koo pingi lamo lao kiŋi peteyamo dokona peyami. Papala nakamame lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko embame wambu mendeme yuu gii akalisa rema dusipana mee bange anatuŋu lao lakandenge mendepe akali mendepe keta bange piso see nana lao emba keta iki piso sinya. Mendeme dopa pii nara ramo doko mena laene palenge yuwale dokona pyambwaro lao mawa pii doko pepa pyao palyii kande, leyami.
\p Dokopa kiŋi dokome isingi lao, Waa, pii ama porai doko yuu Mitia dee yuu Pesape dolapona lowa pii doko alowa pii nange dopale, leya.
\p 
\v 13 Leyamo dokopa nakamame kiŋi doko lamaiyuo, Daniele yuu Juta range doko yaki nyuo karapusi ingyuo epeyamo dokome emba kiŋi andakeŋe lao rape rape laa nalyamo dee mawa pii emba lao palyiinyi doko warombo soo pii nalyamoko. Baa yuu peparae yuu gii mendakinya yuu remasa lao ateŋa lao karamo, leyami.
\p 
\v 14 Pii leyaminyi doko kiŋi dokome sepala baa mona randapala kata wakale mendena Daniele baa kyawa lete nyipuli lao koto kareya. Baa kapa pipala lete nyero lao ene makande pyuo suu pyao kareyamo pao neta anda peya.
\v 15 Dokopa akali dupwa kiŋi peteyamo dokona dee kamba epapala baa lamaiyuo lao, Emba kiŋi doko silini. Yuu Mitia yuu Pesa dolapona lowa letamuli pyuo mawa pii kiŋimi waso lenge doko dee alowa pii nara ingilyamo, leyami.
\p 
\v 16 Dokopa kiŋi dokome akali dupwa kando lamaiyuo, Daniele baa mena laene palenge yuwale dokona minyuo pao pyambwala pena leya. Lapala baame Daniele kando lao, Embena Anatu, embame yulu rape rape lao pyakamingi dokome emba kyawa lete nyinya leya.
\v 17 Dokopa nakamame kana kameya mende nyepala yuwale kambu ketae dokona upi lao reteyami. Dokopa mendeme Daniele baa pao kyawa lete nyuo neta nyisaramiŋi lapala kiŋi banya namba dokomepe banya akali mupwa dupwana namba dupwamepe isa roo yale dupwame pepa pyao make dopale ingyuo rambu lanyi palyiya.
\v 18 Kiŋi doko kapu kyuo banya anda papala yuu gii kukwa dokopa baa nenge naa nao dee male laa nao baa kamame luu kuki mendepe pali naya.
\p 
\v 19 Yangama neta pyakayamo dokopa kiŋi baa sipurapala mena laene palenge yuwale dokona waiya lao peya.
\v 20 Baa repeta papala dokopa pii poraiyuo yamarangyuo lao, Daniele Anatu lete karenge embame banya yulu pyakamingi dokome mena laene dupwa naa nana lao emba kyawa lete nyuo nyisapyase? piso soo leya.\fig Namba keta koo mende pali nao doko baa singi.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="6:22"\fig*
\p 
\v 21 Leyamo dokopa Danieleme isingi lao, Emba kiŋi andake karalu karena.
\v 22 Mena laene dupwame namba randa joo naa nana lao nakamana nenge kata dupwa upi larami lao Anatumi banya aŋala dupwa peeyapya. Dokona namba keta koo mende pali nao dee nambame emba kiŋi andake doko keta koo mende pii nao pingi doko baa singi dokome dopa pipya, leya.
\p 
\v 23 Leyamo dokopa kiŋi baa ama rae wakasa maipala mena laene yuwale dokona Daniele baa nyisa ipyuo nyinya leya. Dokopa nakamame baa neta ipyuo nyepala kandeyaminyi dokopa baa Anatu kapa ingingi lao poraiyuo suu piyamo dokome baa mendasape randa nyuope pii nayamo kandeyami.
\v 24 Dokopa kiŋi dokome mawa pii retapala akali lapome Daniele kando koo pilyamo leyaminyi dupwape dee dupwana enda wanepe dupwa peparae pyasapala mena laene palenge yuwale dokona nyuo pyambunya leya. Pyambuyaminyi dokopa nakama angi doko koko papa nayaminyipa wambo mena laene dupwame kapusapala nakamana kuli dupwa peparae roo pyao muu muu piyami.
\p 
\v 25 Dokopa kiŋi Darisimi wambu yuu muu dupwanape wambu rara dupwanape dee pii wakale lenge paleyaminyi dupwanape peparae nakama pepa pyao maiyuo yako leto, leya.
\v 26 Nambame mawa pii dake reto lalu lao leto. Yuu muu nambame isingi dupwana wambu peparaeme Danielena Anatu doko mupwa lao suu pyao pakame kumuo rape rape lao laramuli pyuo kararami ingilyamo.
\q1 Baa Anatu lete karalu karenge.
\q1 Dee baame iso karo puu para.
\q1 Banya kiŋi yulu doko kamame kokwa see narami.
\q1 Dee banya porainya renge doko kamame ote pii nara.
\q1 
\v 27 Baame wambu randa nyilyaminyi dokopa kyawa lete nyuo nyisingi.
\q1 Baame wambumi kando mona nembako yulu akalimi pii nange dupwa
\q1 yake pandanape isa yuunyape pingi.
\q1 Baame Daniele mena laene dupwame kapa pyao naa narami lao kyawa lete nyipya,
\m leya.
\p 
\v 28 Doko Darisi baa kiŋi karo dee Sairose yuu Pesa range doko kiŋi karo piyamo dokopa Daniele baa akali andake angingyuo kapa palyuo kareya.
\c 7
\s1 Danieleme Mena Kisima Pii Repa Repa Pyuo Kandeya Doko
\p 
\v 1 Ee kana mupwa dokopa akali Belesasa baa kiŋi ingyuo yuu Bapilone dokona kareya dokopa namba Danieleme kombeya pipala kukwa dokopa pii repa repa pyuo kandeyo. Kandapala kombeya angi doko pepana pyao reteyo. Kukwa dokopa angi dake kandeyo doko dee pyasi palamo.
\p 
\v 2 Yuu muu kipwa kipwa dupwana peparae piso poo raiya andake minyapala ipwa kota doko pyao kupyalya kupyana piya.
\v 3 Piyamo dokopa mena kisima mendare ingya nange rara wakale wakale dusipa ipwa kota dokona piso sipurao epeyami.
\v 4 Mena dusipana mupwa doko mena laene yale ingiya. Ingiyamopape yaka kambe ingyuo papake kareya. Doko namba kando peteyono dokopa papake dolapo kondo yuku nyisa epeya. Dokopa mena doko nyuo minyalyapala akali dopale ingyuo roya karena leya. Enakana akalinya suu pingi renge doko baa maiya.
\p 
\v 5 Nambame mena lapo doko kandeyo. Doko baa mena beya yale ingyapala banya kenge kimbu dolapome roya kareya. Karapala banya nenge dokona kanya dolapona parali kuli rema kapusaro kareya. Dokopa pii mendeme baa lamaiyuo, Minju malu mee emba nalana lao suu pilinyili pyuo nape, leya.
\p 
\v 6 Namba mee dokona kandaroko siyunu dokopa mena mendeko epeyamo kandeyo. Doko mena lepete lenge dopale. Dopale ingiyamopape banya mata dokona yakana papake dopale kisima kareya. Dee banya kyawa kisimako kareya. Baa keta porainya renge paleyamo dokome wambu iso karara ingiya.
\p 
\v 7 Dee dopako pyuo isaro karo kandeyono dokopa mena kisima doko kandeyo. Doko ama porai wakasa dokome wambunya mona pakanyi pyambwara ingiya. Baa nenge kameya isa ane yale karenge dokome wambu dupwa pyao lungu ranyi palyapala ketae dokona kalyuo para ingiya. Baa mena dolomana mendare ingya napala banya ayemba dokona nenge akalisa kareya.
\v 8 Dopa piyamopa nambame nenge dusipa kandaroko siyunu dokopa kanya dokona nenge kuki mende potemo epeyamo kandeyo. Kandeyono dokome wambo nenge rema kareyami dusipa pyao lalyinyi nembeya. Doko baa wambunya lenge renge dopale renge. Dee wambunya kambu dopale banya kambu kareya. Baame pii dupwa range mupwa lao lakanda minya minya pyuo leya.
\s1 Mendali Palu Karalu Karenge Mendena Pii Repa Repa Piya Doko
\p 
\v 9 Namba kandeyono dokopa petenge isa dupwa singinyili pyuo reteyamo kandeyo. Dokopa mendali palu karalu karenge doko baa petenge isa mendena peteya. Banya komau doko ama kewa wakasa lao randake kapa yale dee banya kyawa doko puu ulu karo pisa nange dopale. Banya petenge isa dokona isare uliyapu ingyuo rao dee isa petengena kimbu ipyuo minyuo penge dusipana isare ingyuo rao piyako.
\v 10 Doko rao range palu lombo nyisa epeya. Dokopa wambu ama malu mee banya yulu pyakamyuo dee wambu ama malu wakasame banya lenge kambu siyamo dokona roya kareyami. Dupwana kote pii kanda soo lalana buku dupwa lumbuyami.
\p 
\v 11 Namba kandeyono dokopa nenge kuki dokome baa range mupwa lao suu pyao pii ketae palyuo laoko kareyamo siyu. Kando iso kareyono dokopa mena kisima doko pyapala banya yongo doko isare uliyapu dokona pyambuo kiso kokwa sinyi nembeyami.
\v 12 Mena menge dupwana renge porai dupwa nyisa nyiya. Nyiyamopape nakama yuu gii kuki lama palu karena lao yaki nyiya.
\p 
\v 13 Yuu gii kukwa dokopa kombeya pyuo pii repa repa piyunu dokonako wambu yale mende kandeyo. Baa namba kareyono dokona repeta epapala kopa dokome bolotoko lapala baa mendali lete palu karalu karenge doko peteyamo dokona peyamopa baa apipi lao polo leyami.
\v 14 Dokopa wambu yuu muu peparae palenge dupwamepe pii wakale wakale lenge dupwamepe wambu rara peparae dupwamepe banya yulu pyakamirami lao baa porainya rengepe kingi ketae pyambuo lakandenge rengepe dee kiŋinya porai rengepe dusipa maiya. Banya porainya renge doko sulu sera dee banya kiŋi yulu doko ota nara ingiya.
\s1 Pii Repa Repa Piyamo Dupwana Renge Doko Polo Leya
\p 
\v 15 Namba pii repa repa pyuo kandeyono dokome namba pakanyi pyambuyamosa namba yamarangyuo kareyo.
\v 16 Dokopa namba wambu roya kareyaminyi dokona papala mendeme renge dupwa peparae polo langinya lao piso siyu. Dokona lao baame renge angi doko akipi lao langiya.
\v 17 Dokopa baame lao, Doko doo mena kisima dusipa suu pyao doko kiŋinya isingi yulu kisimako isa yuu dakena sipurao sera.
\v 18 Seramopa Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokona wambu dupwa kiŋinya porai renge nyepala minyaro karalu kararami, leya.
\p 
\v 19 Leyamo dokopa nambame mena kisima doko mena menge dusipa yale daa dokona lao konda pyuo selana suu piyu. Wambu pakanyi pyambuo isa ane yale nenge karenge dee kone kana yale kinjipa wanga karenge dupwame wambu dupwa pyao lungu ranyi palyapala ketae dokona kalyuo para ingiyamo dokona lao selana suu piyu.
\v 20 Dee banya ayemba dokona nenge akalisa epeyamo dusipana lao dee mendaki enakana epeya dokome nenge dolomana rema pyao lalyiyamo dokona lao selana suu piyu. Nenge enakana epeyamo doko lenge rao nenge kata soo pingindeme range ketae pyambuo lakandeya. Doloma paka piyamopape baa paka wakasa pingipya dokona renge lama kaname selanako suu piyu.
\p 
\v 21 Namba kandoko peteyono dokopa doo nenge dokome Anatunya wambu pipya yanda pipala nakama pyao isa palyiya.
\v 22 Dokopa mende lete palu karalu karenge doko epeya. Epapala Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokona wambu dupwa keta anjiki pyuo kote leya. Yuu gii doko Anatunya wambu dupwa kiŋinya porai renge doko nyerami lao pyaka siya.
\p 
\v 23 Dake renge angi doko namba polo langyuo jiya. Mena kisima doko kiŋinya isingi yulu kisima doko isa yuu dokona sera. Dokopa kiŋinya isingi yulu doloma nyuo isa palyuo doko wakale mendereko ingyuo sera. Dokome yuu muu peparae isa palyaramopa pyao injo kalyuo sinjimu ingyarami.
\v 24 Menana nenge akalisa dusipa suu pyao doko kiŋi akali akalisa kiŋinya isingi yulu dokona sipurao pirami. Dokopa kiŋi wakale mende sipurao karara. Doko baa kiŋi wambo karenge dupwa yale daa. Baa kiŋi rara wakale ingyuo karara. Karapala kiŋi rema dusipa pyao nembara.
\v 25 Baame Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa doko kando kamba lapala Anatunya wambu dupwa randa maiyuo kopetame isara. Dopa pipala baame nakamana misinya mawa piipi nenge malu palyuo lakando nao petenge yuu giipi alowa pinya piramo dokopa Anatunya wambu dupwa ee kana rema dee kanya ingyuo banya porai dokome isaramopa isarena kararami.
\v 26 Dokopa yake pandana kote singi doko kote soo pisara dokome banya porai renge doko nyisa nyepala pyao kokwa soo nembalu nembo nembara.
\v 27 Isa yuunya kiŋinya isingi yulu dokona yulu andakepe porai rengepe dupwa Anatu Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokona wambu dupwa nyuo maira. Mairamo dokopa isa yuunya akali mupwa karenge dupwame nakamana pii warombo soo yulu pyakamyuo kararaminyi dokopa kiŋinya porai renge nakama keta palira doko ota nalu nara.
\p 
\v 28 Dokona kombeya pii repa repa angi doko dakena ote. Namba lenge kambu yongo nembapala wakasa pakayo. Dopa pyuo pakapala kombeya angi pii repa repa piyunu dusipa peparae kame see nao namba range suu pyaro kareyo.
\s3 8:1-27 Mitia wambupi Pesa wambupi dupwa iso kareyaminyipa piso pao Andioke Epipanese kiŋi kareyamo doko isa peyamopa apa piramo dupwa Daniele baa pii repa repa piyamo dokona kandeya.
\c 9
\s1 Danieleme Banya Wambu Dupwana Lao Ateŋa Lakamiya
\p 
\v 1 Akali Darisi yuu Mitia range Sekesena ikinyingi doko kiŋi ingyuo yuu Bapilone iso kareya.
\v 2 Ee kana mupwa dokona akali baa kiŋi ingyuo kareyamo dokopa namba Danieleme buku poo pyasi dokona mana nyuo kareyo. Doko ee kana akalisa yanda ipingi dusipana yuu Jerusaleme doko kwaeyo momo nao paraŋa lao poropeta Jeremaya lamaiyamuli pyuo mana nyiyu.
\v 3 Dokopa namba kumanda piso wapungi komau wapuo nenge wasaka pyuo peena piso Kamongo Anatu lao ateŋa poraiyuo lao baa piso sokondali pyuo peteyo.
\v 4 Nambana wambu dupwana koo dupwa kame sakaminya lao nambana Kamongo Anatu kando ateŋa lakamiyu.
\p Nambame lao, Kamongo Anatu emba kamame andake. Namwame emba ketae pyambuo rape rape lao lakando karamano. Emba embena kana minyuo lalu lao lenge pii doko suu pyao minyaro karenge. Dee wambu lapome emba mona reto embame pii lengenyili pyuo pingi dupwa embame mona retalu reto retenge.
\p 
\v 5 Namwa yulu koo pingi. Namwa koo dokome kopetame pyuo karenge. Embame namwa mawa pii langyuo dopa pipwa dapa pipwa leene dupwa namwame kamba lao mata joo peyama. Dee embame yulu rolae lasaka pii dupwa yaki nyuo kaeyama.
\v 6 Embena kendemande akali poropeta dupwame embena kingi dokona lao namwana kiŋi akalipi akali mupwape rora ambasupi dee namwana wambu peparaepe lamaingi dokopa namwa see nalu nayama.
\v 7 Emba Kamongo yuu peparae rolae pyuo karapinyipape namwa yulu koo pyuo range keta elya nyuo karamano. Namwa wambu yuu Juta palengepe yuu Jerusaleme palengepe dee Isaraele wambu peparaepe emba yaki nyuo kaeyama. Dokona lao embame repeta nanesape dupwana palu pena lao minyuo muu raleya lao nembee dupwame dopa pyuo kareyama.
\v 8 Namwana kiŋipi akali mupwape rora ambasupi dupwame yulu elya pingi dupwa pyuo dee Kamongo ema kando yulu koo pyuo kareyami.
\v 9 Namwame emba kando koo pyuo mona kana poko mata jiyamanopape embame sakame kumuo kame sakame kumuo kame sakao karenge.
\v 10 Embena kendemande poropeta dupwa keta lowa pii namwa jiinyi dokome laramuli pyuo palipwa lao namwa langipinyipape Kamongo Anatu namwame embena pii doko soo nyii nayama.
\v 11 Isaraele wambu peparaeme embena lowa doko kamba lapala embame lapinyi dokona selena wangu laka nayami. Namwame emba kando koo piyamanosa koo keta palena lenge pii dupwa embena kendemande Mosesena lowa dokona pyasi palamo dupwa embame namwa keta palena leene.
\v 12 Namwa iso karenge akali dupwape dee namwape keta mende piru leene doko mee pii. Dokona lao yuu taone isa yuu dakena silyaminyi dupwa pyao kokwa soo nembenepape embame Jerusaleme kamame wakasako ingyuo randa maiyuo pyao kokwa sinyi nembee.
\v 13 Mosesena lowa dokona randa nyerami lao lapyamo dusipa pepare namwa jii. Jiinyipape kamame epapu Kamongo Anatu namwana koo dupwa yaki nyuo panda embena pii kinyi angi dokona moko minyuo pao emba rae mainyi pyambwalana lao suu pyaa nayama.
\v 14 Emba namwana Kamongo Anatu doko yuu peparae rolae pingi dokome namwa randa jelana rapa rapa pipala angi randa jii kande. Dopa piinyipape namwame embena pii sili see nale lao kareyama.
\v 15 Namwana Kamongo Anatu, yuu Isipi piso embena wambu dupwa lanyuo epeene dokome embena porai renge doko lasaka pii. Dokona lao wambu dupwame embena porai renge dokona lao mee suu pyaro karaminyi. Dopa piinyipa namwame kopetame pyuo yulu koo pyuo karamano.
\v 16 Wamba dokopa emba namwa pipya pyamalyuo nyiso karenge. Dokona lao Jerusaleme pipya imbuo karalu kara napipi. Jerusaleme embena yuu taone doko. Dee embena yuu kyau poo pyasi. Namwana koo dupwanape dee namwana rora ambasu dupwana yulu koo piyaminyi dokona wambu yuu liti wakale wakale maki palenge dupwa peparaeme namwa kilya kandelyaminyi.
\v 17 Anatu nambana ateŋa piso sokondali pyuo leto doko sepe. Sepala embena tembole anda kokwa siyamo doko karengenyili pyuo elya pepe. Emba Anatuŋu lao wambu peparaeme soo nyinyaleŋe dokona tembole anda doko kamba elya pepe.
\v 18 Anatu namwana pii sepe. Sepala namwa randa aki nyilyaminyi lao kandape. Yuu taone dokona embena kingi singi dokona wambu dupwa randa nyilyaminyi doko kandape. Namwa rolae pyuo karamwandena daa. Embame sakame kumuo nyisingi dokome namwa emba kando ateŋa letamano.
\v 19 Kamongo, namwana ateŋa sakape. Sakapala Kamongo namwana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakape. Kamongo namwana pii sepala namwa keta yulu keyange mende pyakape. Wambu peparaeme emba Anatu lao soo nyinyaleŋe dokona mende pinya suu pilini doko waiya lao pepe. Yuu taone dake embena. Dee wambu dae karenge dupwa embenako.
\s1 Rengya Pira Leyamo Dokona Geperieleme Polo Lamaiya
\p 
\v 20 Nambame nambana Kamongo Anatu doko kando ateŋa lao nambana Isaraele wambu dupwana koo dupwa polo lakamyuo dee nambana koo dupwa polo lamaiyuo banya tembole anda poo pyasi doko karengenyili pyuo kamba elya pinya lao piso sokondali piyu.
\v 21 Namba ateŋa pyao piso dokopa aŋala Geperiele kombeya wambo pii repa repa piyunu dokona kandeyono doko namba peteyono mare dokona bii lao epeyamo kandeyo. Doko kukwa mena pyao kiso maingi doko mairama yuu gii ingiyamopa kandeyo.
\v 22 Baame polo lao, Daniele rengya mende pira dokona emba soo gisilase lao nyiso langyala epelyo, leya.
\v 23 Embame kanda soo Anatu kando ateŋa lao piso sokondali pyuo leene dokopa baame emba isingi yano piya. Anatumi emba mona retenge dokome ateŋa isingi yano pyapyamo pii doko langyala epelyo. Dokona nambame pii repa repa angi piinyi dokona polo langirunu dokopa emba elya kalo soo pisipi.
\p 
\v 24 Ee kana andete kisima ipisu akalisa mange mendaki (490) epo paparamopa Anatumi embena wambupi embena yuu taone poo pyasipi koo keta moko nyero lao rombo palyiya. Yuu gii dokopa koo dupwa kame sakaramo dokopa wambu dupwa rolae pyuo karalu kararami. Dopa piramo dokopa pii repa repa piinyi dokope dee rengya mende pira lao poropeta pii leyamo dokope angi kinyi ingyuo para. Paramo dokopa tembole anda doko dee yapasi ingyuo karara.
\v 25 Dokona pii dake soo nyepe. Yuu Jerusaleme kamba elya pinya lao lamairamo yuu gii dokona piso pao Anatumi akali mende kyawa ingyuo rombo palyiyamo doko kararamo yuu gii dokopa ee kana akalisa kisima ipisu mange mendaki (49) dusipa epo para. Dokopa enakana yuu taone Jerusalemepe kata sukusa singi dupwape kana kame porai awali lao karengepe dupwa elya piraminyipa ee kana malu (434) karara. Kararamopape ee kana dusipana randa malu epara.
\v 26 Ee kana 434 epo paparamopa nakamame Anatunya rombo palyisi akali mupwa doko mee langa pyao kumakarami. Dokopa wambu iso karenge akali mupwa mendena ami yanda singi dupwame epapala yuu taonepe tembole andape dupwa pyao lalyuo kokwa serami. Anatumi yanda pyuo randa epo pira lao reteyamo doko ipwa kopetame palyuo epenge dopale ingyuo lumwa pyuo epara.
\v 27 Wambu iso karenge akali dokome wambu malu dupwa pipya ee kana yanda ipingi nembo mona mendaki palyuo pii walengena lao kararami. Ee kana rema dee kanya dusa ingyuo baame mena pyao kiso maingipi bange maingipi dupwa ote pyuo kaena lara. Dopa pyuo kaena lapala baame mee bange anatu kingimi wasisi mende tembole anda pinjingi londe dokona ketae pisara. Pisaramo doko pisaramoko pao akali pisiyamo dokona lao Anatumi yuu gii lumwa pyuo randa mairu lao rapa rapa pyuo reteyamo doko pyaka seramo dokopa otara.
\s3 10:1—12:13 Wamba pii repa repa piyamo doko Daniele dee kando dee renge lapo opetae konda pyuo kando piya. 
